         return false;
         }}</script>
```

:::
:::


It is also possible to create a list of answers for students to choose:


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
check_question("banana", options = c("apple", "banana", "bread"), type = "select")
```

::: {.cell-output-display}

